<div class="thumbinner" style="width:177px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Terry_fox_statue.jpg" class="image" title="The Terry Fox memorial statue, Simon Fraser University."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/32/Terry_fox_statue.jpg/175px-Terry_fox_statue.jpg" width="175" height="262" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
